文<br />\n<br />\n簡介：相傳，西貢的山頭上有「結界」，即似百慕達三角的神秘異空間，令不少行山人士神秘失蹤&hellip;&hellip;警長獨自行山後人間蒸發，他做社工的女兒耿耿於懷，堅持要尋找真相，但多年來苦無結果。他失蹤滿七年之際，一個瘋瘋癲癲的行山用品店主突然宣稱，他在山上的結界撿到警長的委任證！女社工沿著結界傳說追查，決心尋回父親，怪事卻接二連三發生。電影改編自過百萬瀏覽的本地網絡小說，一探香港最神秘的結界傳說。熟悉的西貢山頭和舊式公共屋邨場景，融入香港都市血案，令人不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWI4Si46eB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBWI4Si46eB0&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=6a38633d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWI4Si46eB0</a>"},{"pid":"a28a40c93c214bb520deb244d811800fcfe005b9","tid":1723611,"uid":14802,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"午夜狂熱馬拉松睇完<br />\n<br />\n𠝹凳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beffe82a5c43853bf6a36c51183f319a26224c98","tid":1723611,"uid":50216,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"呢兩個禮拜好多戲想睇<br />\n但真係冇心情入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334b94bdd689bad01bcf8db0281f262b9678e597","tid":1723611,"uid":44674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔伏，低成本算係咁<br />\n係結局說教味太重"},{"pid":"456ee7aaf7e5cb0784cf3e9f3aa3870b665cf84f","tid":1723611,"uid":277506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"beffe82a5c43853bf6a36c51183f319a26224c98","tid":1723611,"uid":50216,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"呢兩個禮拜好多戲想睇<br />\n但真係冇心情入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"本身都想睇呢套同黑魔后<br />\n，但呢排同你一樣無乜心情睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b669d58f5653733129fa86a64e41ee7e083f450b","tid":1723611,"uid":189534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"334b94bdd689bad01bcf8db0281f262b9678e597","tid":1723611,"uid":4